<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870303-0173 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:American Can Co.</HL><DD> 03/03/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS AC </IN><DATELINE> AMERICAN CAN CO. (Greenwich, Conn.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    James A. Long,formerly senior vice president, was named to the new post ofexecutive vice president in charge of mergers andacquisitions for this financial services and specialtyretailing concern. David I. Chemerow, formerly vicepresident, was named to the new post of senior vice presidentand corporate controller. American Can said the moves came aspart of a restructuring, which has included the shedding ofits packaging operations and a refocusing as a financialservices company.</TEXT></DOC>